cast.overview: A successful mod photographer in London whose world is bounded by fashion, pop music, marijuana, and easy sex, feels his life is boring and despairing. But in the course of a single day he unknowingly captures a death on film.
cast.title: Blow-Up
cast.character: Girl Dancing In Ricky Tick Club (uncredited)

details.biography: Janet Street-Porter, CBE is an English media personality, journalist and broadcaster. She was editor for two years of The Independent on Sunday, but relinquished the job to become editor-at-large in 2002.
details.name: Janet Street-Porter
